{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"SVGAElement.target","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/SVGAElement/target","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/SVGAElement\"><code>SVGAElement</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriedades</summary><ol><li><em><code>target</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herança:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGGraphicsElement\"><code>SVGGraphicsElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGElement\"><code>SVGElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>O&nbsp;<code><strong>SVGAElement.target</strong></code>&nbsp;propriedade somente ler de <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/SVGAElement\"><code>SVGAElement</code></a> retorna&nbsp;um objeto <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGAnimatedString\"><code>SVGAnimatedString</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> que especifica a porção de um alvo sendo ele \"window\", \"frame\" ou&nbsp;\"pane\" no qual um documento será aberto quando o link for acionado.</p>\n\n<p>Esta propriedade é usada quando existem dois ou mais possiveis alvos(destinos)&nbsp;para o documento, por exemplo, quando o documento pai é um arquivo .html ou .xhtml com varias telas (multi-frame).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\"><code><em>myLink</em>.target = '<em>value</em>';</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor","title":"Valor","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Um <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGAnimatedString\"><code>SVGAnimatedString</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> indica&nbsp;o destino final do recurso que abre o documento assim que&nbsp;o link é acionado.</p>\n\n<p>Valores para&nbsp;<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>target</code></a> você pode ver&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2011/REC-SVG11-20110816/linking.html#AElementTargetAttribute\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">aqui</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O código&nbsp;é foi retirado de&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SVGAElement#example\">\"SVGAElement example code\"</a></p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> linkRef <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'a'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nlinkRef<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'_blank'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Specification</td>\n   <td>Status</td>\n   <td>Comment</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/text.html#InterfaceSVGAElement\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Scalable Vector Graphics (SVG) 1.1 (Second Edition)<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'target' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recomendação</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com o navegador","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>9.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/target\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">target (en-US)</a></code></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com o navegador","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O SVGAElement.target propriedade somente ler de SVGAElement retorna um objeto SVGAnimatedString (en-US) que especifica a porção de um alvo sendo ele \"window\", \"frame\" ou \"pane\" no qual um documento será aberto quando o link for acionado.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"SVGAElement.t